org.dataconservancy.packaging.tool.model.ontologies

Class DcsBoPackageOntology

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dataconservancy.packaging.tool.model.ontologies.DcsBoPackageOntology

  • public class DcsBoPackageOntology
extends Object
    This class provides setup and create an instance of DcsBoPackageOntology. It is intended to use to create a serialized ontology to be used with Package Tool, needs to be updated according to the most current ontology.
